    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Type of documentary film that shares many of the same characteristics with cinéma vérité, but lacks the smooth, spontaneous camera movements typically associated with that style. Instead, camera presence is down played and long-take shots film using a stationary tripod are more typical.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047990/Beaver, Dictionary of film terms (1994)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Soort documentaire die veel dezelfde kenmerken vertoont als cinéma vérité, echter zonder de soepele en spontane camerabewegingen die meestal worden toegeschreven die met die stroming worden geassocieerd. Bij direct cinema valt de aanwezigheid van de camera nauwelijks op, met vaak lange shots vanaf een vast statief.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>這類型的電影和真實電影（cinéma vérité）有許多共同的特色，但缺乏真實電影風格中的平順自然的典型攝影機運鏡方式。攝影機的存在反而並非那麼受到重視，而運用固定三角架的長鏡頭影片倒是更為典型。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
